{
  "_comment_about_this_file": "Example InstantGMP MCP config with LITERAL values, for AI clients that do not expand environment variables. Replace the three REPLACE_ME values with your real InstantGMP base URL, API user, and API password. The base URL must NOT include a trailing slash.",

